## Demo on how to load another file
- name: Demo on Load another file
  hosts: all


  tasks:
    - name: Print Hello World
      ansible.builtin.debug:
        msg: Hello World

    - name: Include task list in play
      ansible.builtin.include_tasks:
        file: universe.yml




Here we want to load the universe.yml file to the yml file as an example to test how to include task to ansible






##google How to load yaml file ansible
include_tasks module